169
00:07:30,620 --> 00:07:32,220
 What you need to know is that he was writing

170
00:07:32,220 --> 00:07:34,940
 to a group of young believers in a city called Colossae.

171
00:07:34,940 --> 00:07:37,020
 Colossae wasn't an especially large city

