 but what it was, was especially diverse.

174
00:07:41,740 --> 00:07:43,340
 It was diverse ethnically.

175
00:07:43,340 --> 00:07:45,540
 There were Phrygians as well as Greeks

176
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:47,660
 and some Jews living there within the city.

177
00:07:47,660 --> 00:07:51,100
 And it was also ethnic, it was also diverse philosophically,

178
00:07:51,100 --> 00:07:52,460
 which actually raises the issue

179
00:07:52,460 --> 00:07:53,580
 that Paul is going to address,

180
00:07:53,580 --> 00:07:55,460
 which I'll unpack for you in a minute.

181
00:07:55,460 --> 00:07:57,480
 But what you see is that he's writing

182
00:07:57,480 --> 00:08:00,500
 to a group of young Christians, young believers,

183
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:02,980
 that have placed their faith in Jesus Christ,

184
00:08:02,980 --> 00:08:07,980
 that have made the ultimate decision to go all in with God.

185
00:08:07,980 --> 00:08:10,380
 And yet now they're appropriately at a place

186
00:08:10,380 --> 00:08:12,620
 that many of you may find yourself sitting in.

187
00:08:12,620 --> 00:08:13,700
 What's next?

188
00:08:13,700 --> 00:08:14,860
 Like, how do I get better?

189
00:08:14,860 --> 00:08:16,820
 What does it look like for me to advance as an individual,

190
00:08:16,820 --> 00:08:18,340
 to progress through this life,

191
00:08:18,340 --> 00:08:20,940
 for me to achieve all the fullness of God,

192
00:08:20,940 --> 00:08:23,300
 all the fullness that God is offering me

193
00:08:23,300 --> 00:08:24,740
 while I'm here on this earth?

194
00:08:24,740 --> 00:08:26,140
 How do I do it?

195
00:08:26,140 --> 00:08:28,460
 What steps do I take from here?

196
00:08:28,460 --> 00:08:30,780
 This is the question these believers are asking,

197
00:08:30,780 --> 00:08:32,300
 and you may be asking yourself.

198
00:08:32,300 --> 00:08:34,780
 And to these believers,

199
00:08:34,780 --> 00:08:38,380
 this backdrop of Colossae,

200
00:08:38,380 --> 00:08:42,020
 a city diverse in philosophy and ideology

201
00:08:42,020 --> 00:08:44,980
 and riddled with so much different tradition

