210
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:16,220
 He learns that this is the case

211
00:09:16,220 --> 00:09:17,580
 for this young group of believers.

212
00:09:17,580 --> 00:09:19,260
 And so he writes this letter to them

213
00:09:19,260 --> 00:09:23,380
 to clarify for them very specifically with one voice

214
00:09:23,380 --> 00:09:24,400
