215
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:26,180
 what it looks like to grow in Christ like this,

216
00:09:26,180 --> 00:09:29,940
 what it looks like to mature and move forward in life.

217
00:09:29,940 --> 00:09:32,620
 And so what he says,

218
00:09:32,620 --> 00:09:36,320
 and the main idea of this entire letter

219
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:41,320
 is that if you want maturity in life,

220
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:43,740
 you need clarity of Christ.

221
00:09:43,740 --> 00:09:44,900
 That's Paul's point.

222
00:09:44,900 --> 00:09:47,140
 That's what this entire letter is about.

223
00:09:47,140 --> 00:09:50,040
 If you want maturity in life, you need clarity of Christ.

224
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:52,940
 You don't need spiritual mysticism and special knowledge

225
00:09:52,940 --> 00:09:55,820
 and some path to a superior existence

226
00:09:55,820 --> 00:09:57,380
 or some new moral ethic.

227
00:09:57,380 --> 00:09:59,140
 You don't need any of this other stuff

228
00:09:59,140 --> 00:09:59,980
 that people are telling you.

229
00:09:59,980 --> 00:10:03,140
 What you need is you need greater clarity of him.

230
00:10:03,140 --> 00:10:06,400
