00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,340
 where we unpacked what?

233
00:10:10,340 --> 00:10:13,860
 The one thing that God wants most for you,

234
00:10:13,860 --> 00:10:15,700
 which is to see him.

235
00:10:15,700 --> 00:10:17,420
 And the reason we're studying Colossians

236
00:10:17,420 --> 00:10:19,540
 is because this is the natural next step.

237
00:10:19,540 --> 00:10:22,740
 Now that you see him, what then happens?

238
00:10:22,740 --> 00:10:24,140
 What then takes place?

239
00:10:24,140 --> 00:10:28,300
 Your clarity of him produces a maturity in you.

240
00:10:28,300 --> 00:10:32,140
 This is why as Paul writes the book of Colossians,

241
00:10:32,140 --> 00:10:33,780
 he presents what is quite possibly

