00:10:38,420 --> 00:10:43,060
 He paints a picture of Jesus with an unbridled beauty

244
00:10:43,060 --> 00:10:45,560
 and out of this world beauty,

245
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:48,660
 because he wants them and he wants you to know

246
00:10:48,660 --> 00:10:50,460
 there's no one like him.

247
00:10:50,460 --> 00:10:53,940
 There's plenty and all the more to find within him.

248
00:10:53,940 --> 00:10:56,600
 You just need to see him clearly.

249
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:58,580
 And in so doing, you'll see yourself.

250
00:10:58,580 --> 00:11:00,460
 That's what he's going to unpack for us.

