00:22:21,120 --> 00:22:24,720
 If you asked her for a report

531
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:29,920
 on the quality of my leadership during our dating history,

532
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:32,800
 I'd have anything but straight A's.

