00:22:47,780 --> 00:22:49,620
 but a really poor dating reality.

537
00:22:49,620 --> 00:22:53,400
 I wonder how many of us could say

538
00:22:53,400 --> 00:22:56,960
 the same is true for us tonight, just with respect to faith.

539
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:59,840
 That our faith mentality, man, it's really good.

540
00:22:59,840 --> 00:23:01,880
 Like I could sit down and I could chop it up

541
00:23:01,880 --> 00:23:04,320
 with the best of them at the coffee shop.

